1161→		// to lookup the metadata required to process the samples. Not used by Prometheus itself.
1162→		// TODO(gouthamve) We're using a dedicated context because using the parentCtx caused a memory
1163→		// leak. We should ideally fix the main leak. See: https://github.com/prometheus/prometheus/pull/10590
